No pops, cracks or hisses - SoundSport Free headphones maintain a strong and reliable wireless signal, whether your phone is in your hand, nearby gym bag or strapped to your arm. They fit comfortably and securely, so you can sprint, jump, lift, climb, twist and turn without worry. And the earbuds are designed with water-repellent mesh, ensuring that rain and sweat stay out, so all you hear is the music that motivates you.    No Wires. Calls, Commands and Easy Control Take a call, play or pause tracks, change the volume or access your phone’s Siri or your Google Assistant right from the earbud. Charge it on the Go The magnetized case protects your earbuds and holds them in place while they travel in your gym bag. And while it holds them, it charges them, too.
